{"word":"G5030 - ταχέως - tachéōs - takh-eh'-oce - Hastily","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ταχέως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tachéōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">takh-eh'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hastily</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சீக்கிரமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"quickly, shortly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G5036 - ταχύς - tachýs - takh-oos'/5036\">G5036</a>; <i>briefly</i>, that is, (in time) <i>speedily</i>, or (in manner) <i>rapidly:</i> - hastily, quickly, shortly, soon, suddenly.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}